Package org.webcycle.hexml

Interface Summary
iCollection a sequential list of objects, implemented by non-atomic parsable objects (those which can contain others).
iHexmlAttributes common interface to all Hexml features that collections of attributes.
iHexmlFeature Names all Hexml feature objects.
iHexmlObject the interface to all parsable things
iParseContext  
 

Class Summary
BasicAtom An atomic entity with attributes
BasicContainer a basic implementation of an object that has both attributes and elements.
hexml The primary utility class; methods for streaming XML with hexml types.
HexmlElements a container of elements, with default functionality for toString() and unrecognizedText().
HexmlObject Simple implementation for parsable objects, providing basic utility functions for xmlish parsable objects, such as parsing/printing attribute lists, etc.
HexmlString A container of the form <tag>text</tag> where text is an opaque string.
HFAttributeTable A collection of attributes as a java.util.Hashtable
HFElementVector Storage for elements in a Vector.
ParseContextImpl A simple iParseContext implementation.
Parser A simple xml-like parser base class which uses a Trie data structure to recognize tag names and map them to java classes.
Vocabulary a parser's vocabulary.
